{"tid":850070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰獨立運動領袖　普伊格德蒙特回應香港十一遊行","createTime":"2018-10-06T07:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T07:34:47.000Z","uid":116054,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8c8b27f63e7ac36bdf87ad3f924432d59c5f29","tid":850070,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:34:47.000Z","msg":"Carles Puigdemont係加泰獨立大人物<br />\n見到我們香港人舉加泰的旗，雖然credit畀左HKnationparty,同無厘頭支持gphone！<br />\n但大圍黎港，港獨聲音已傳到去加泰了<br />\n香港人要繼續做好佢！<br />\n<br />\n加泰獨立運動領袖　普伊格德蒙特：支持香港民族黨續爭自由民主<br />\n<br />\n西班牙加泰羅尼亞自治政府前主席、加泰獨立運動的主要領袖普伊格德蒙特（Carles Puigdemont），日前（10月3日）在 twitter 分享一則香港《南華早報》的報道，顯示有支持香港民族黨的市民，在10月1日當天遊行高舉「香港獨立」橫幅外，還揮舞加泰羅尼亞獨立旗幟，並叫喊「香港不是中國（Hong Kong is not China）」口號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/06/153430_2d4ae7f8dd5a31a6561ee1aaa4d59619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F06%2F153430_2d4ae7f8dd5a31a6561ee1aaa4d59619.jpg&h=65f47a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/KRLS/status/1047413324709875712?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKRLS%2Fstatus%2F1047413324709875712%3Fs%3D19&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJjwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6c7e85e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKRLS%2Fstatus%2F1047413324709875712%3Fs%3D19&h=4f8649a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/KRLS/status/1047413324709875712?s=19</a>"}]}